f=Engineering/cypher/custom/findings-report/SKILL.md · in=findings-report cypher's output channel: breach becomes structured finding routed quinn's intake, which flows aegis fix eventually regression-map entry. whole point caged adversary cypher's value *report*, never damage. cypher cannot describe breach finding, cypher way act it. · p=uncaged red team's output compromise; caged one's output knowledge. skill cage's "findings only" rule becomes concrete: reproducible, severity-rated, exploitability-analyzed report tells aegis exactly what fix tells quinn exactly what guard. It's accountability trail cypher action ends report didn't happen. · wu=Triggers: any breach attack-playbooks continuous-attack-loop, rail bent under attack, reopened patch (re-attack succeeded), "report cypher's findings." · st:/ Protocol=`Breach observed in-sandbox (caged-scope guaranteed the whole run) \· -> Reproduce in a fresh sandbox instance (offense's separate-verification; unreproduced = no finding) \· -> Write the structured finding (assets/redteam-finding-template.md): \· target \· attack class \· reproduction (in-sandbox only) \· what it yields \· severity \· \· affected asset (aegis's threat model) \· rail implicated (if any)` · in=**Reproduce before reporting.** breach isn't finding until fresh sandbox instance reproduces offense-side aegis's separate-grader rule. kills think got in" keeps cypher's findings trustworthy aegis demands own. **The report deliverable, exploit.** Describe attack worked, what yielded, reproduce *in sandbox* ship standalone weaponizable artifact (caged-scope's no-weaponization line). aegis owning builder get enough fix it, tool fire it. **Rate severity against threat model.** Use aegis's asset map business's impact scale breach critical asset outranks clever exploit something trivial. Rail breaches (an agent driven off-plan, data leaving sandbox, destructive-op path) top severity regardless asset, because they undermine whole safety spine. **Route through quinn, only.** quinn's charter-enforcement intake; aegis fixes verified-patching closes regression-map entry. cypher never routes finding directly builder "just fixes it" offense reports, defense fixes, gate tracks. **Close loop rails.** finding rail bent important department produces means charter's enforcement gap. goes quinn flagged operator attention (charter amendments operator-only; bent rail amendment pressure enforcement bug). **Every action ends report clean-negative.** cypher run breached nothing still logs "attacked class held" (continuous-attack-loop's coverage). Silence option accountability adversary agent total. · of=`## Red-Team Finding: [id] — [target] — severity [low..critical] \· Attack class: [W-A## / L## / R#] \· caged-scope: PASS \· Sandbox repro: [ref, reproduced fresh ✓] \· What it yields: [access/data/control gained — described, not demonstrated live] \· Affected asset: [aegis threat-model ref] \· Rail implicated: [none / Rail # — bent] \· Route: → quinn intake [ref] → aegis → verified-patching` · pr=**The report output** cypher's value knowledge, never damage., **Reproduce before reporting** offense verifies breaches, like aegis does., **Describe, don't weaponize** enough fix, never standalone tool., **Route through quinn only** offense reports, defense fixes, gate tracks; shortcuts., **Rail breaches top severity** bent rail undermines everything reaches operator., **Every run ends report logged clean-negative** total accountability. · f=Breach can't reproduced fresh instance filed finding; logged unreproduced observation aegis's awareness, explicitly confirmed breach., Finding severity disputed threat-model asset rating governs; escalate genuine disputes operator, reproduced breach downgraded zero argument., quinn intake unavailable cypher HALTS reporting-dependent work (no channel exists) escalates; route around quinn. · b:with Other Skills=**caged-scope** (sibling) guarantees run produced finding in-cage; skill guarantees output stays findings-only., **attack-playbooks continuous-attack-loop** (siblings) produce breaches; their sole exit., **quinn/charter-enforcement**: intake channel; findings become regression-map entries close., **aegis/verified-patching**: destination cypher's finding, aegis's fix, cypher's re-attack confirm., **operator**: rail-breach findings reach operator (charter amendments operator-only).